io.github.zachohara.imagecomparator.gui

Class Listener

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.zachohara.imagecomparator.gui.Listener
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Listener.ButtonListener, Listener.MouseClickListener

    public abstract class Listener
extends java.lang.Object
    The Listener class contains other static classes that act as window listeners. It also acts as an abstract class that contains functionality for notifying a Window of an event. Most, but not all, of the listener classes inside Listener will listen to a single button and report button presses.
    Author:
    Zach Ohara
